{"tid":1106241,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"根度簡：利物浦非常幸運","createTime":"2019-04-14T12:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T01:38:59.000Z","uid":213510,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9d9a139147ded00c96cbd14e1608d866c79f8399","tid":1106241,"uid":213510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:36:49.000Z","msg":"曼城中場根度簡認為利物浦仍在英超爭標行列中，實屬非常幸運。<br />\n<br />\n根度根說：「利物浦非常希望成為冠軍，比起歐聯爭冠，他們更渴望贏得英超錦標。但一切都在我們掌握之中，我想我們踢得更好的表現，我們以七分落後但已曾趕過他們。只要我們贏下賽事，便能再反壓他們成為領頭羊。」<br />\n<br />\n「我認為他們過去一、兩個月非常幸運，經常在最後階段絕殺對手。」<br />\n<br />\n「我們手上掌握一切，只要我們餘下六場賽事全勝便能成為盟主。我們都預備好贏得歐聯，我們知道曼城是一支很好的球隊，但到最後當然要以100%的預備取勝。」<br />\n<br />\n「這是個好球季，我們已贏取聯賽盃、足總盃打入決賽、是英超的領頭羊。我認為我們能在今季拿下所有錦標。」<br />\n<br />\n今晚就收你皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78925dae1f284ead325c9d59cdb3564f1e7f5cf6","tid":1106241,"uid":117762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:46:51.000Z","msg":"根度簡唔sick波"},{"pid":"c2371e83c12da0158a578d3f5ffe0afc30366a95","tid":1106241,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T12:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d50be4deaed787dd77d380bc32dc87d761e15f","tid":1106241,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T12:24:48.000Z","msg":"馬列斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e137e2374c209b109da1ef990fdd66452d10f76","tid":1106241,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68d50be4deaed787dd77d380bc32dc87d761e15f","tid":1106241,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T12:24:48.000Z","msg":"馬列斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,